- Installed polybar
  - required dependencies: sudo apt install build-essential git cmake cmake-data pkg-config libcairo2-dev libxcb1-dev libxcb-util0-dev libxcb-randr0-dev libxcb-composite0-dev python-xcbgen xcb-proto libxcb-image0-dev libxcb-ewmh-dev libxcb-icccm4-dev
  - optional dependencies: sudo apt install libxcb-xkb-dev libxcb-cursor-dev libasound2-dev libpulse-dev libjsoncpp-dev libmpdclient-dev libnl-genl-3-dev libcurl4-openssl-dev
- Install check from source, prereq for rofi below
  - sudo apt install automake autoconf libtool pkg-config texinfo
  - use autoreconf --install in root
- Install rofi from source
  - sudo apt install bison flex librsvg2-dev
  - install `dependency` from source https://github.com/libcheck/check.git